      section
        h2.bullet WHY SUBLIME TEXT?
        h3.bullet here's a short list of ST's features

      section
        h2.bullet Customizeable
        h3.bullet Preferences > Settings - *
        h3.bullet everything is in JSON so it's easy to understand
        hr
        pre.bullet
          code.language-javascript.
            "bold_folder_labels": true,
            "caret_style": "phase",
            "highlight_line": true,
            "highlight_modified_tabs": true,
