      section
        h3.bullet <em>back to features...</em>

      section
        h2.bullet Minimap
        h3.bullet sometimes we get lost in our own mess

      section
        h3.bullet auto completion
        h3.bullet brace/bracket/tag matching
        h3.bullet expand/collapse scopes
        h3.bullet build/compile code inside the editor

      section
        h2.bullet Multiselection
        h3.bullet CTRL + D
        h3.bullet CTRL + click
        h3.bullet ALT + SHIFT + up or down
        h3.bullet "Find All"

      section
        h2.bullet Keyboard Shortcuts
        h3.bullet delete line: CTRL + SHIFT + K
        h3.bullet duplicate line: CTRL + SHIFT + D
        h3.bullet swap line(s): CTRL + SHIFT + up or down

      section
        h2.bullet Find/Replace
        h3.bullet find: CTRL + F
        h3.bullet replace: CTRL + H
        h3.bullet find in files: CTRL + SHIFT + F

      section
        h2.bullet Panes, groups and screen modes
        h3.bullet pane management: ALT + SHIFT + 1 to 5
        h3.bullet pane switching: CTRL + 1 to 5
        h3.bullet zen/distraction-free mode: SHIFT + F11
        h3.bullet sidebar: CTRL + KB

      section
        h2.bullet Bookmarks
        h3.bullet CTRL + F2
        h3.bullet F2 and SHIFT + F2

      section
        h2.bullet Command Palette
        h3.bullet Go To Anything for Settings
        h3.bullet <strong>CTRL + SHIFT + P</strong>

      section
        h2.bullet Snippets / Macros

      section
        h2.bullet Go To Anything
        h3.bullet ..or how to browse your code like a ninja
        h3.bullet <strong>CTRL + P</strong>
        h3.bullet :123 go to line 123 or CTRL+G
        h3.bullet @function_name go to function blah
        h3.bullet file.py go to file.py
        h3.bullet file.py:123 go figure! ;)

      section
        h2.bullet Packages
        h3.bullet ST packages = game changer
        h3.bullet <a target="_blank" href="https://sublime.wbond.net/">https://sublime.wbond.net/</a>

      section
        h2.bullet Search in Project
        h3.bullet Let's you use <strong>ack</strong> or <strong>ag</strong> inside ST
        h3.bullet <a href="https://sublime.wbond.net/packages/Search%20in%20Project">https://sublime.wbond.net/packages/Search%20in%20Project</a>

      section
        h2.bullet SublimeLinter

